title: ☞2x2 South Austin Apartment Home!☜
posting_body: ['🌳TRAMOR HUNTERS GLEN🌳', '*If you sign up with our preferred renters insurance provider, ePremium, we can waive $100 off the security deposit, as well as waive the $200 pet deposits if you have pets!', '🐾 Mention this ad!*', '🔒APARTMENT FEATURES🔒', 'Pictures are of actual unit - available August!', 'You will have 883 sqft and a covered private patio!', 'The unit is located on the first floor and is going for $1735/month.', "The apartment is Google Fiber-ready with a jack, but if you'd like to opt for a different provider feel free!", 'Water is allocated (usually about $35/person) and electricity is set up through the City of Austin', 'Your new home will have a washer/dryer HOOKUPS, stainless steel appliances, and hardwood floors!', '✿COMMUNITY FEATURES✿', '- No breed restrictions/weight limits', '- Courtyard areas', '- Swimming pool', '- Property security', '- Near transportation + very walkable!', '- 24/7 maintenance', '- Guest parking', '- Off-street parking', '- Covered balcony', '- Popular area by South Austin', '- Private and tucked away location!', 'Contact info:', 'Abi', 'Tramor at Hunters Glen']
